summary: Crissy, The half elf, half redguard preset
descriptionHtml: Simply drop it in Steam>steamapps>common>Skyrim>Data>SKSE>Plugins>CharGen>Presets. I may make her into a companion, but I'm not that good with modding. Requires RaceMenu and ApachiiSkyHair. The face texture is from Better Females By Bella. Load the preset by either starting a new game, or typing the console command "showracemenu". Click "Presets" on the top right, then press F9 and load it.
author: GenerallyTso
